 p(r,n) = \max\left\{\frac r n, \frac r n p(r-1,n-1) + \frac{n-r} n p(r,n-1)\right\}. 
 p(r,n) = \max\left\{\frac r n, \frac r n \frac{r-1}{n-1}+\frac{n-r}n\frac{r}{n-1} \right\} = \max\left\{\frac r n, \frac{nr-r}{n(n-1)}\right\}  = \frac r n. 
